It’s Sobisco Smashers Malda vs Murshidabad Kings in Bengal Pro T20 League Season 2 opener

The Bengal Pro T20 League Season 2 will commence on June 11 at the iconic Eden Gardens with Sobisco Smashers Malda taking on Murshidabad Kings in the opening match. 

Following the opening day’s match, the men’s league will see double headers being played till June 24. The league matches will conclude on 25th June.

The semifinals will be a double-header affair at the Eden Gardens to be played on June 26th from 1pm and 7pm onwards.

The grand final will be held at the Eden Gardens on June 28 from 7 pm onwards.
